		mixin tpcModal(id)
			if id=="agd1"
				p The 5G NR market is growing rapidly in many regions where network operators are using combined low-band, mid-band and mmW spectrum to provide 5G enhanced mobile broadband (eMBB) services and fixed wireless access (FWA).  As pointed by Grand View Research “The value of 5G services in 2020 was measured at $41.48 billion, a figure which is forecast to grow at a compound annual growth rate of 46.2% between 2021 and 2028.” Among 3 major 5G frequency bands, mmW is viewed as a critical step toward delivering full 5G’s potential and enable Gbps download speed with very low latency. Commercial mmW 5G networks have already been launched in multiple countries, including the U.S., Japan and South Korea. Other nations such as Italy, Finland and Australia are releasing mmW spectrum for 5G or are about to follow suit. The launch of the mmW Apple iPhone 12 and iPhone 13 series also provide a timely boost to the adoption of mmW. According to GSMA “Operators that underestimate the role of mmWave in the short term run the risk of finding themselves at a disadvantage to competitors when offering 5G services.”  Anokiwave will share the latest the mmw market progress and present the latest product of the company. 

			else if id=="agd2"
				p 隨著Apple iPhone 12系列的熱賣，敲響了28GHz與39GHz雙頻毫米波頻段的爭戰。當新生代5G手機支援這些頻段，同時O-RAN開放式架構的提出與OTIC認證的推動，使得5G毫米波相關產品推出與商品化的時程大幅提前，也帶動了包括台灣廠商在內5G毫米波新的市場商機。
				p 本次針對5G毫米波小型基站在無線接取與前端模組設計，量測與校正上的挑戰進行討論，同時探討廠商在投入5G毫米波相關產品的布局，以及未來在5G毫米波前端模組開發及驗證上所面臨的機會與挑戰。
				p 把5G毫米波化作遊戲介面，在整個城市交通網路上新建高架快速解決問題。了解5G毫米波市場佈局，在精確的時間攻入，取得第一張入場券，不塞車不卡關，搶得市場先機。
				div 【在本場演講裡，將了解到】
				ul.pl-3(style="list-style-type:none")
					li Q1. 對於5G毫米波市場前景的看法? 預期何時市場起飛, 大量商用?
					li Q2. 5G毫米波市場起飛的契機為何? 有哪些新的市場機會?
					li Q3. 對於即將起飛的5G毫米波市場, NXP, Anokiwave 與円通科技各自的佈局為何? 各有何優勢?
			
			else if id=="agd3"
				p 產線計畫的經濟學一直都是獲利中不可忽略的部分，隨著5G NR標準橫跨了  FR1與FR2頻段,伴隨更大的頻寬與更高的頻率，測試方法與儀器設備也隨著標準的變化增加，在市場競爭下，高性價比與高度彈性配置的測試方案，將會是有效降低製造成本的關鍵
				div 這次主題討論我們將討論
				ul
					li 5G NR FR1/FR2測試方案
					li 5G FR2 量產型CATR 天線緊縮場
					li 5G NR FR1/FR2 量產型信令測試方案

			else if id=="agd4"
				p Ready for the rising tide of 5G rollouts, NXP has a set of programmable baseband processors for the 5G access edge. To delivering a programmable baseband for open, intelligent 5G, NXP provides the 5GNR L1 Reference Enablement Package to bring fast time-to-market development environment for the customers. The 5GNR L1 Reference Application (also referred to as RefApp) is meant to provide a starting reference for developing 5G NR L1 software for the Layerscape Access SoCs. The purpose of the RefApp is first and foremost to show how this functionality is achieved and open the path towards including this functionality in a real product. In this session, NXP will present the most recent development with Anokiwave RF technology in serving 5G-NR FR2 mmWave use cases. Key functions to be introduced in the session including:
				ol
					li L1T toolkit
					li DPDK fronthaul support with compression/decompress support
					li FreeRTOS new L1 refAPP TDD support
					li Synchronization, frame alignment and VCXO correction

		mixin spkModal(id)
